highlights.text: Sabrina Carpenter has the most spots on Top Songs Norway. “Tears” is the highest at #19.
“Du lyg” by Ruben is the highest new entry on Top Songs Norway at #17.
“The Night We Met” by Lord Huron has been on Top Songs Norway the longest, at 142 weeks straight.
“Her kommer Bjørnis” by Brannbamsen Bjørnis is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Norway, up 79 spots at #80.
